d in production; in dev a generated value is persisted to the data dir"},"1052":{"id":"/guides/installation-64","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"`SECRETS_ENC_KEY`"},"1053":{"id":"/guides/installation-65","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"32-byte key (base64/hex) for the encrypted secrets store. Keep it safe — rotating it makes stored secrets unreadable"},"1054":{"id":"/guides/installation-66","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"`RUNYARD_HUB_BOOTSTRAP_TOKEN`"},"1055":{"id":"/guides/installation-67","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"Optional pre-seeded bootstrap admin/runner token (containers); on host installs one is generated into the data dir"},"1056":{"id":"/guides/installation-68","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"`RUNYARD_HUB_INSTANCE_NAME`"},"1057":{"id":"/guides/installation-69","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"Display name of the deployment (default `Runyard`)"},"1058":{"id":"/guides/installation-70","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"Runner:"},"1059":{"id":"/guides/installation-71","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"Variable"},"1060":{"id":"/guides/installation-72","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/guides/installation#environment-variables","content":"Meaning"},"1061":{"id":"/guides/installation-73","page_id":"/guides/installation","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"